name: 3. Data Clustering And Modelling
content:
Model Used:

Classification Model is trained to identify possible fraudulent Claims submitted.


Features Used for Classification Model training:

  • Organization
  • Gender
  • City
  • State
  • Encounter
  • Amount
  • Method
  • Duration
  • Transfers
  • Outstanding


Target data used:

  • fraud_flag


Classification Model used:

  • H2O Distributed Random Forest
